{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4cc1c848-a12c-4f71-ae8b-2503c37bc758","content":"Yes, you **will** run into compatibility issues. MSTest v3 dropped support for some of your target frameworks:\n\n- **`net5.0`** — .NET 5 is not supported in MSTest v3. You need to upgrade to **`net6.0`** or later.\n- **`net462`** — .NET Framework older than 4.6.2 is dropped, but 4.6.2 itself is still supported, so this one is fine.\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — .NET Core 3.1 is not supported in MSTest v3. You need to upgrade to **`net6.0`** or later.\n\n**Before migrating**, update your `TargetFrameworks` to replace the unsupported TFMs. For example:\n\n```\nnet8.0;net462\n```\n\nWould you like me to invoke the full MSTest v2→v3 migration skill to handle the upgrade for you?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"794a42e5-25ab-43f0-9a5e-7c41c8a95c14","outputTokens":225,"requestId":"CFD7:1FFE72:65DF4C5:71E2554:69EC26AF"},"id":"0d5084c7-e44e-4f38-9a5d-a834f7baa6b4","timestamp":"2026-04-25T02:28:04.654Z","parentId":"5e4ed62d-208e-4e21-915c-0c5a60ba669d"}
